1. DEFINITIONS
================================================================================

"Software" means the ALICE-SDF Unity/Unreal plugins, editor tools, and
streaming components covered by this license.

"Game" means an interactive entertainment application distributed to end users,
where the Software is used as a component for rendering or content creation.

"Infrastructure Service" means any service that:
  (a) Provides the Software's functionality to third parties as a service
      (SaaS, PaaS, IaaS), or
  (b) Uses the Software to operate a multi-user platform with more than
      10,000 monthly active users, or
  (c) Generates more than $1,000,000 USD annual revenue from services
      that incorporate the Software.

